WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:25.800
The ocean floor rises five miles to the shores of what people call the Seven Mile Miracle.

2
00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:31.800
What would it be like to be born on this island?

3
00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:37.800
To grow up on these shores?

4
00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:43.800
To witness this water every day?

5
00:00:43.800 --> 00:00:47.800
You're about to meet someone who did.

6
00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:17.800
All the harm done for sure.

7
00:01:17.800 --> 00:01:24.800
Three tears for all the souls below.

8
00:01:24.800 --> 00:01:30.800
One day we made them to fear.

9
00:01:30.800 --> 00:01:36.800
Learned them all with all my faith.

10
00:01:43.800 --> 00:02:09.800
Who are you, my dear?

11
00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:16.800
I am the Antichrist.

12
00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:22.800
Fire in the sky.

13
00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:29.800
Into your heart.

14
00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:35.800
Who are you, my dear?

15
00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:42.800
I am the Antichrist.

16
00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:48.800
Fire in the sky.

17
